Instructions:

(1) Create a bot within the Discord developer portal
(2) Create a Discord server
(3) Upload the emoji files to the server (not the developer app), keeping their specific names
(4) Create a Github repo, and upload this code into it
(5) Create a cloud server, pull the Gihub code, and run this program using the start command "python main.py"

Environmental variables:

POLYGON_API_KEY=
SERVER_ID=
TOKEN=

Resources:

https://discord.com/developers/applications
